org.openimaj.math.geometry.transforms.residuals

Class AlgebraicResidual2d<M extends Model<Point2d,Point2d> & MatrixTransformProvider>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.math.geometry.transforms.residuals.AlgebraicResidual2d<M>
  • Type Parameters:
    M -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResidualCalculator<Point2d,Point2d,M>

    public class AlgebraicResidual2d<M extends Model<Point2d,Point2d> & MatrixTransformProvider>
extends Object
implements ResidualCalculator<Point2d,Point2d,M>
    Compute the algebraic residuals of points mapped by a 2d homogeneous transform (i.e. a 3x3 transform matrix). This is equivalent to the residuals minimised when using the Direct Linear Transform method (i.e. minimising |Ah|) used for estimating the transform.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
